{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>For The Hive \u2013 A Brutal, Gory Insect Survival Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>For The Hive</strong> is an intense insect survival simulation blending exploration, role-playing, and strategic warfare. Enter a vast, living world where every creature fights to survive\u2014just like you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Brutal, Gory Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survival isn\u2019t just about running\u2014it\u2019s about fighting. <strong>Rip enemies apart, decapitate foes, and dismember rivals</strong> in fast-paced, bloody battles. Every encounter is a struggle for dominance, with no mercy for the weak.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Beautiful and Immersive World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Venture through a stunning, ever-changing ecosystem with a full <strong>day-night cycle</strong>. Climb towering trees, scale plants and rocks, or dive into the depths of hidden caves. Every inch of the world is yours to explore\u2014but danger lurks everywhere.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Start as a Tiny Larva \u2013 Grow Into a Legend</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Begin life as a helpless <strong>larva</strong> and fight to survive as you <strong>grow into a mighty queen, a towering beetle, or one of over 20 different species</strong>. Each insect has its own unique abilities, strengths, and playstyle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Mating &amp; Legacy \u2013 Build Your Family</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survival isn\u2019t just about you\u2014<strong>find a mate, build your colony, and continue your bloodline</strong>. Play as your offspring and shape the future of your species, ensuring your lineage thrives for generations.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Join a Faction \u2013 Wage War</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ally yourself with powerful insect factions and take part in <strong>massive territorial battles</strong>. Whether you conquer, defend, or forge alliances, your choices will shape the world around you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Live the Life of an Insect</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hunt for food, gather resources, and stay alive by eating, sleeping, and even <strong>cleaning yourself</strong>. From lone survivalist to colony leader, carve your place in a world where only the fittest thrive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you have what it takes to rule the wild?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747630/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739568352","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747630/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739568352","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747630/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739568352","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747630/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739568352","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>For The Hive \u2013 A Brutal, Gory Insect Survival Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>For The Hive</strong> is an intense insect survival simulation blending exploration, role-playing, and strategic warfare. Enter a vast, living world where every creature fights to survive\u2014just like you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Brutal, Gory Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survival isn\u2019t just about running\u2014it\u2019s about fighting. <strong>Rip enemies apart, decapitate foes, and dismember rivals</strong> in fast-paced, bloody battles. Every encounter is a struggle for dominance, with no mercy for the weak.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Beautiful and Immersive World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Venture through a stunning, ever-